    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me over the years. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, so it\u2019s ready to hit the road with a new owner today! It looks great, runs smoothly, and is just waiting for its next adventure. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still feels fresh, come check it out\u2014I\u2019d love to show it to you!",
      "price": 33500.0,
